# Project Context

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/Radix |
| State | TanStack Query (server state) · Zustand (UI state only) |
| Forms | Zod validators · Server Actions |
| HTTP | Axios (`apiAxios`) client-side · fetch (`apiClient`) server-side |
| Notifications | `sonner` — `toast.success()` / `toast.error()` |
| Animation | framer-motion (installed — never remove) |
| Backend | Express 5, Drizzle ORM, Neon PostgreSQL |
| Auth | JWT httpOnly cookies — `access_token` (15min) + `refresh_token` (7d) |
| Email | Resend (`RESEND_API_KEY`) |
| Storage | AWS S3 presigned URLs (B6 — pending) |
| Deploy | Frontend → Vercel · Backend → Railway |

## Environment Variables

### Frontend (`zafora-frontend/.env.local`)
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` — Express backend base URL
- `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET`, `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET`

### Backend (`zafora-backend/.env`)
- `DATABASE_URL` — Neon PostgreSQL connection string
- `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET`, `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET`
- `RESEND_API_KEY`, `RESEND_FROM_EMAIL`
- `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` — CORS whitelist
- `ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@zaforaholding.com`

